data.description: Immaculate 5 Bedroom + Office w/ Finished Basement make this young (2020) 2 Story Home one to checkout! Great layout begins w/ 2 Story Entry w/Tile Floor that Opens to Living RM. Great Kitchen w/ 42” Cabinets, Quartz Ctr, Lg Walk-In Pantry, Sink Window Looks Out to Flat, Fenced Backyard, & Lg Informal Din that Leads to Family RM & Sliding Door to Patio. Fam RM has Beautiful Stone Fireplace. Office is Tucked away for Less Distraction. Laundry & ½ Bath also on Main. Primary Suite is Lg w/ Walk-In Closet, DBL Vanity w/Quartz Ctrs, DBL Head Walk-In Tile Shower & Tile Flr. 3 Other BRs are all Good Size w/ Good Size Closets. Full Bath w/Tile Surround Bath & Flr. Professionally Finished Basement w/ LVP Flr throughout, a Large En-Suite Bedroom w/ ¾ Bath & Walk-In Closet, a Big Rec RM, & Storage RM. 3 Car Garage is Finished w/ Epoxy Floor & All Attached Storage Shelving Stays w/ Home. Close to Offutt, Shopping & HWY 75
